    "The first LSTM layer has 20 units and returns sequences.",
    "It takes input of shape (1, 56), where 1 represents the time step and 56 is the number of features.",
    "The second LSTM layer also has 20 units and returns sequences.",
    "The final Dense layer has 10 units with softmax activation, which is suitable for multiclass classification.",
    "The model is compiled with sparse_categorical_crossentropy as the loss function and adam as the optimizer."
